Modify the Inferno Community Distribution Plan rules to the following, starting on Sunday, 6/5/2022
- The minimum individual amount is reduced from 1GB to 100MB
- Up to 50 wallets that hit the minimum will ALWAYS be rewarded each week (unless non one hits the minimum).
- Their reward amount would be cut in half if <50 wallets reach the minimum.
- All partial amounts are rounded up
- If 50 wallets hit the minimum, users receive the full weekly reward defined in the previous rule set.
